e feel.</li>\r\n	<li>Some people are just more comfortable in their day to day shoes.</li>\r\n	<li>Let''s face it, nobody wants to rent golf shoes...</li>\r\n</ul>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-revision-14', '', '', '2010-04-27 04:06:43', '2010-04-27 04:06:43', '', 2, 'http://localhost/2-revision-14', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
